      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Albums of photographs of famous personages in the arts. Some photographs are formal
            head and shoulder type, others are full length. Many are of actors portrayed in the
            roles they played in well known plays. One volume is an alphabetical index to the
            photograph albums.</p>
      </scopecontent>
