      <arrangement>
         <head>COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT</head>
         <p>There are twenty-six volumes labelled A-Z and twenty-nine volumes numbered 1-29, as well as an index volume. The index volume is alphabetical and gives the letter or number of the volume in which the photographs may be found. They are not in any particular order in the volume.</p>
      </arrangement>
